sc_cat_item.description:
THE PARKING HANGER IS ONLY VALID AT 5601 FISHERS LANE, NOT ON THE NIH CAMPUS

For questions or contact information, see https://inside.niaid.nih.gov/working-niaid/5601-parking-program-rules-regulations.

Requests for overnight parking must have the 5601 Fishers Lane Overnight Parking Form attached for approval (OVERNIGHT VEHICLE REGISTRATION FORM (nih.gov)). Once approved, the signed form will be provided via email. This form must be printed and displayed at all times while your vehicle is parked in the 5601 Fishers Lane parking garage or surface lot. "

DO NOT complete this form if you are a Transhare or Bicycle Program participant. You are not eligible to receive a parking hanger. See 5601 Parking Program Rules and Regulations for temporary parking options. Vanpool operators are eligible for a parking hanger for the van only.
